lead_paragraph: India celebrated their 500th test in style when they overcame New Zealand's final dogged resistance with mesmeric spin and masterful swing to claim the series opener by 197 runs on Monday.

headline.print_headline: India Thump New Zealand to Celebrate 500th Test in Style
